      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 4Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \nP100 as 100ms\nP90 AS 50MS\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n75M users \n2.5M DAU \n\n1 user on avg does 5 search then \nwith 2.5M we will have 10.25M search per day i.e. 118 Search\nper / sec \nSearch QPS = 118 query/sec\nCreaterBusiness = 10 query/sec\n\nData:\nThere will be 200-300M globally ",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "lHeLS_0Z5wIRvcGIWWaQA",
      "originalText": "NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS: 4Min\n\n1} LATENCY: \nP100 as 100ms\nP90 AS 50MS\n\n2} SCALABILITY:\n75M users \n2.5M DAU \n\n1 user on avg does 5 search then \nwith 2.5M we will have 10.25M search per day i.e. 118 Search per / sec \nSearch QPS = 118 query/sec\nCreaterBusiness = 10 query/sec\n\nData:\nThere will be 200-300M globally ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
