      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "API-Endpoints: 5Min\n\n1] API_NAME:  POST - CreateBusiness\nA} Input: create_business(user_id, latitude, longitude)\nB} Output:-\n\n2] API_NAME:  GET\nA} Input: search_nearby(user_id, latitude, longitude,\nradius)\nB} Output:- [{\nbusiness_id, business_name, rating, distance, category...\n}]\n\n",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "MRIPLh6vB6a5v5dU-hedj",
      "originalText": "API-Endpoints: 5Min\n\n1] API_NAME:  POST - CreateBusiness\nA} Input: create_business(user_id, latitude, longitude)\nB} Output:-\n\n2] API_NAME:  GET\nA} Input: search_nearby(user_id, latitude, longitude, radius)\nB} Output:- [{\nbusiness_id, business_name, rating, distance, category...\n}]\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
