      "updated": 1773726937289,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 41.299244448442074,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "text": "1] User provides (lat, lon, radius)\n2] Convert circle to a bounding box\n3] Traverse only quadtree nodes whose rectangles intersect that box\n4] Collect candidate business points from matching leaves\n5] Compute Haversine distance i.e. great-circle distance between 2 points on earth\n6] Keep only those within radius\n7] Rank and return the results (e.g., by distance, rating, relevance, popularity).",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1] User provides (lat, lon, radius)\n2] Convert circle to a bounding box\n3] Traverse only quadtree nodes whose rectangles intersect that box\n4] Collect candidate business points from matching leaves\n5] Compute Haversine distance i.e. great-circle distance between 2 points on earth\n6] Keep only those within radius\n7] Rank and return the results (e.g., by distance, rating, relevance, popularity).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
